      "side": 1,
      "message": "I really want to deprecate task_num and kill the task_num assignment cron. Instead, we should use a string field like instance_id or container_id, etc. Custom schemas are ready for use in tsmon, and here is a demo\n: https://cs.chromium.org/chromium/infra/go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/common/tsmon/examples/beep/dummy_project/dummy_project.proto?g\u003d0\n\nWe need to create and design a new proto and setup a retention policy for it. Let me know if you like to give it a try",
