      "side": 1,
      "message": "monarch.Acqusitions.Task[\u0027hostname\u0027] is already being used to store the version of the serving binary in gae_ts_mon. It\u0027s definitely bad choice, but that\u0027s the main usage the field.\n\nThe logical meaning of a field for a Target schema should remain the same regardless of the application. If not, then a different schema should be used.\nFor example, monarch.GKE.Task[\u0027hostname\u0027] can have different meaning than monarch.Acqusitions.Task[\u0027hostname\u0027] does.",
